metadata.name: SafetyFirst Emerge Token
metadata.description:
So here it is: the token of your dreams!!1! Hold one of these babies* and get yourself some tasty, tasty art. The good digital shiznits. Them pictures and stuff with the moving and the glitching and the serene, meditative stillness. Or something!

Is there any inherent value here? I mean, no, but also kind of yes? Sure. Depends how you look at it. If you own one of these, you're gonna get some stuff. That, yes, we can agree on.

Tokens!

*tokens
